snippet.title: Amber Heard: Johnny Depp used me as a punchbag, court hears | ITV News
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has insisted that she did not have an affair with the tech entrepreneur Elon Musk during her marriage to Johnny Depp.

Asked by Mr Depp’s lawyers if she had a relationship with him, the 34-year-old actor replied: “No - not that it matters.”

It was suggested by Mr Depp’s legal team that he was not “illogically jealous”, that he had a reason to suspect that she was having an illicit relationship with Mr Musk while they were still married. 

She said that she only started to communicate with Elon Musk in 2016.
